//| FIX#MERGE_C4b: OnTP2Hit SL ladder — add 0.4×ATR buffer          |
//|   ROOT: OnTP1Hit had FIX#MERGE_C4 (0.4×ATR buffer below TP1).  |
//|   OnTP2Hit moved SL to EXACT TP2 price → TP3 runner started     |
